OK, take your right leg, you're going to wrap it around the rope,

00:02:30.300 --> 00:02:34.200
and inside. That's all you're going to do, just do that once or twice.

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:41.720
When you get that foot inside, curl that toe up. Good. One more time like that.

00:02:43.820 --> 00:02:47.100
Good, one more time so it's kind of muscle memory.

